                <item xml:id="addition5" n="5">
                  <locus from="3a"/>
                  <ref target="#handNote6"/>
                  <p>On fol. 3 a there are the remains of a note, showing that this was one of the 250 volumes, procured for the <placeName>convent of S. Mary Deipara</placeName> by the <persName>abbat Moses of Nisibis</persName>, A. Gr. <date when-custom="1243" datingMethod="Seleucid">1243</date>, A.D. <date when="0932" calendar="Gregorian">932</date>.</p>
